        <p class="text-white/40 mb-4 text-sm font-medium">Effective Date: April 1, 2026</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
            Welcome to <strong class="text-white">CalJin AI</strong>. By downloading, installing, accessing, or using
