            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">1. Overview</h2>
                <p class="text-white/70">CalJin AI is an AI-powered calorie tracking and nutrition management
                    application. The App uses artificial intelligence to analyze food images, estimate nutritional
                    values, and provide personalized meal plans based on your health profile.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
